==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lithuanian
<hw>Lith`u*a"ni*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to Lithuania (formerly a principality united with Poland,
then part of the Soviet Union, but since 1992 an independent
nation).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lithuanian</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Lithuanian
<hw>Lith`u*a"ni*an</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A native, or one of the
people, of Lithuania; also, the language of the Lithuanian
people.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lithy</ent>⟦br⟧
